Fisheries (Processing and Handling) Amendment Rules 2020

I make the following rules under the Living Marine Resources Management Act 1995 .

16 November 2020

GUY BARNETT

Minister for Primary Industries and Water

1. Short title
    These rules may be cited as the Fisheries (Processing and Handling) Amendment Rules 2020 .

2. Commencement
    These rules take effect on the day on which their making is notified in the Gazette.

3. Principal Rules
    In these rules, the Fisheries (Processing and Handling) Rules 2010 are referred to as the Principal Rules.

4.
    The amendment effected by this rule has been incorporated into the authorised version of the Fisheries (Processing and Handling) Rules 2010 .

Displayed and numbered in accordance with the Rules Publication Act 1953.

Notified in the Gazette on 2 December 2020

These rules are administered in the Department of Primary Industries, Parks, Water and Environment.
